1.Download and  install Node.js >> npm will automatically install in node.js
2.Check whether its being installed right
   open command prompt: run below commands
   node --version
   np --version
3. run below command
  npm install -g json server
4.add a json file (lets say student.json in this case) and save it in your local
5.Go to that file location and run below command
  json-server student.json
6. SUCCESS!

